"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"据官方消息，Ergo生态网站Sigmaverse新增了一项应用——Ergo Payment Portal（Ergo支付门户）。商家和个人可使用此支付门户就其产品和服务接受ERG付款。该dApp旨在方便小商家和个人使用Ergo支付。它提供了一种在其他应用中整合Ergo或SigUSD支付的方法，允许从URL请求支付。\",\"timestamp\":1639034940,\"title\":\"Ergo支付门户上线\"},\"digest\":\"HXR5blKRfQINKT_8aOOdllQLuObk-Kjbx8Sk-3ATTn8\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x285F0eF323A7F1AF4d512D17e6Beed35791309a9\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"L1g3H9b9lchBINo1K0DBo0UfZ_V6PjYjooLDpexaGLw\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"LdVoT_PxMYaV3xZCWD2jIt26_A0p8lceq4s1UO7uxZQ\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"A220ooxqeKmVTZk3WtMaSYKwG0LG5neBedm0LRS2OYTnP2NeJeCM_j2FV5mPc0xvu8xVpCHjA61xV3NSwiKobg\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x342dbe250a24424d05a4a9716713b3fb8a2b17e8a19d77f60052152c800a713d384ef528d9d2b98995df1e23f1aaec4d127edc6f552fe4f9c989ea80e8ad02bc1c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"L1g3H9b9lchBINo1K0DBo0UfZ_V6PjYjooLDpexaGLw\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"LdVoT_PxMYaV3xZCWD2jIt26_A0p8lceq4s1UO7uxZQ\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"HXR5blKRfQINKT_8aOOdllQLuObk-Kjbx8Sk-3ATTn8\"}"